title: Cloud tests fixes
body:
cloud tests improvements, fixed race condition (jira ticket: SIOS-661), added SwiftKeyApp-Nightly scheme for nightly builds (pretty much -AppStore, minus localization tests)

@tomdixon

title: optimised for ios7 SDK compiled apps on bigger phones, including a stat
body:
Volume II, @tomdixon. Soz.

Tagging @peterholc as well, for the stats stuff and @martin-bussiere for theme stuff (if he's interested). 

FYI - Yes, the multiplier is 0.85 and 0.77 for iPhone 6, 6+ respectively in both orientations, but that is rounded. The actual values were different, hence I wanted to keep the orientation check in there.
